<li id="cite_note-84"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-84">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external autonumber" href="http://www.newkabbalah.com">[3]</a> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120717001420/http://www.newkabbalah.com/">Archived</a> 2012-07-17 at the <a href="/wiki/Wayback_Machine" title="Wayback Machine">Wayback Machine</a> www.newkabbalah.com, <i>Kabbalah and Postmodernism: A Dialogue</i>, Sanford L. Drob, Peter Lang Publishing, 2009</span>
